<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 06:20:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>受伤的拉杜卡努成为最新退出中国公开赛的大牌球员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/injured-raducanu-latest-big-name-pull-out-china-open-2024-09-24/</link><description>前美国公开赛冠军艾玛·拉杜卡努 (Emma Raducanu) 成为最新一位退出中国公开赛的知名选手，此前英国人表示因脚伤将缺席 WTA 1000 赛事。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 06:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/injured-raducanu-latest-big-name-pull-out-china-open-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲高级官员表示摩根大通看好印度和日本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/jpmorgan-bullish-india-japan-top-asia-official-says-2024-09-24/</link><description>美国最大银行摩根大通一位高级官员表示，看好亚洲的印度和日本，但也热衷于将资源配置到受益于“中国加一”战略的东南亚。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 05:48:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/jpmorgan-bullish-india-japan-top-asia-official-says-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国推出大范围降息和其他刺激措施以刺激疲软的经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rolls-out-broad-rate-cuts-other-stimulus-spur-weak-economy-2024-09-24/</link><description>中国周二宣布了一系列措施来支持步履蹒跚的经济、稳定房地产市场并恢复市场信心。消息公布后，股票和债券大幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 04:57:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rolls-out-broad-rate-cuts-other-stimulus-spur-weak-economy-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>G7表示中东局势升级不会给任何人带来好处</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-says-nobody-will-gain-middle-east-escalation-2024-09-24/</link><description>七国集团（G7）主要民主国家的外交部长周一警告称，在中东的行动和反行动有可能将该地区拖入一场更广泛的冲突，而任何国家都不会从中受益。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 04:47:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-says-nobody-will-gain-middle-east-escalation-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：没有火箭筒，但中国最新的刺激措施让人松了一口气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-24/</link><description>Ankur Banerjee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 04:38:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>Interax报道称，俄罗斯和中国军舰进入鄂霍次克海进行演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/russia-china-warships-enter-sea-okhotsk-drills-interax-reports-2024-09-24/</link><description>俄罗斯国际文传电讯社周二援引太平洋舰队新闻部门的消息称，作为海军联合演习的一部分，俄罗斯太平洋舰队和中国海军的一支军舰编队进入西太平洋鄂霍次克海。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 04:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/russia-china-warships-enter-sea-okhotsk-drills-interax-reports-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国推出广泛刺激措施以重振陷入困境的经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-broad-stimulus-measures-revive-economy-2024-09-24/</link><description>央行将把银行必须持有的现金储备量削减50个基点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 03:36:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-broad-stimulus-measures-revive-economy-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国坚定支持黎巴嫩维护安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-firmly-supports-lebanon-safeguarding-its-security-2024-09-24/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周一向黎巴嫩外长布哈比卜表示，中方坚定支持黎巴嫩维护主权和安全，强烈谴责以色列大规模空袭后的违法行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 03:01:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-firmly-supports-lebanon-safeguarding-its-security-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>台湾在网络指控后表示，中国才是真正的黑客，而不是我们</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-are-real-hackers-not-us-taiwan-says-after-cyber-accusations-2024-09-24/</link><description>政府高级官员周二在台北表示，中国才是真正的黑客，而不是台湾，北京对台湾黑客组织的指控是假新闻。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 02:50:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-are-real-hackers-not-us-taiwan-says-after-cyber-accusations-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国大范围降息：投资者的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-investors-react-chinas-broad-rate-cuts-2024-09-24/</link><description>消息公布后，中国股市普遍上涨，债券上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:50:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-investors-react-chinas-broad-rate-cuts-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>计划入股永辉超市 名创优品股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shares-miniso-slump-plans-buy-stake-yonghui-superstores-2024-09-24/</link><description>名创优品集团控股公司表示将入股陷入困境的中国超市运营商永辉超市，周二该公司股价暴跌 39.2% 至 20 港元（2.57 美元）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:47:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shares-miniso-slump-plans-buy-stake-yonghui-superstores-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行推出广泛宽松措施以重振经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-will-cut-banks-reserve-requirement-ratio-by-50-bps-2024-09-24/</link><description>央行将把银行必须持有的现金储备量削减50个基点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:37:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-will-cut-banks-reserve-requirement-ratio-by-50-bps-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国采取扩张性刺激措施，亚洲股市创2-1/2年高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-24/</link><description>受中国广泛刺激措施的鼓舞，亚洲股市周二上涨至两年半以来的最高水平，而对美国进一步降息的预期则令风险情绪高涨，美元承压。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:21:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国新刺激措施和中东紧张局势导致油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-rise-concerns-wider-middle-east-conflict-us-storm-2024-09-24/</link><description>周二，由于最大进口国中国推出新货币刺激措施的消息传出，以及人们担心中东紧张局势升级可能会影响主要产区的供应，而全球最大原油生产国美国正面临一场重大飓风，油价上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:07:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-rise-concerns-wider-middle-east-conflict-us-storm-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>澳洲联储保持鹰派立场，澳元触及2024年新高；中国刺激措施推动人民币升值</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/aussie-dlr-near-2024-high-before-rba-yen-drifts-ueda-awaited-2024-09-24/</link><description>由于央行重申抑制顽固通胀的决心，周二澳元升至今年最高水平，而在中国采取新的刺激措施后，人民币攀升至16个月高点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/aussie-dlr-near-2024-high-before-rba-yen-drifts-ueda-awaited-2024-09-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>